description: An interactive catalogue for Pippa Darbyshire's debut exhibition with @FineNFT. All paintings will be available as authenticated 1/1 editions via hic.link/fine. Browse all 12 paintings and read more about the artist - use the menu icon top left for options (slideshow, dark/light mode etc). It is a responsive design but best viewed on desktop (full screen) since Hic et Nunc's viewport is not too user-friendly on mobile. Navigation with cursor keys also works. Gallery built by @1x1_NFT.
